WEBVTT

01:51.610 --> 01:57.539
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.580 --> 02:01.880
[Episode 5]

02:20.270 --> 02:22.579
O-Oh, it's you!

02:22.600 --> 02:23.920
Why are you here?

02:25.000 --> 02:25.920
I...

02:29.829 --> 02:32.950
Are you delivering cold medicine
to Her Ladyship?

02:34.280 --> 02:35.400
Her Ladyship...

02:35.420 --> 02:37.410
Her Ladyship hasn't fully recovered.

02:37.410 --> 02:38.730
Please excuse me.

02:44.520 --> 02:46.360
Where there is life, there is hope.

02:46.360 --> 02:47.800
I guess the governor is right.

02:47.800 --> 02:49.000
As long as I stay by Her Ladyship's side,

02:49.000 --> 02:50.200
I can see you.

02:50.480 --> 02:51.210
Bear with it.

02:51.220 --> 02:51.870
Wait.

02:54.180 --> 02:55.370
On your waist...

02:58.579 --> 02:59.560
Do you and the governor

02:59.560 --> 03:01.760
have some plan you didn't tell me about?

03:03.110 --> 03:04.390
How do you know?

03:05.040 --> 03:06.300
As perceptive as ever.

03:07.130 --> 03:08.160
But

03:08.190 --> 03:09.470
I can't tell you.

03:09.650 --> 03:11.160
Why can't you tell me?

03:18.550 --> 03:20.010
Actually, it's like this.

03:32.000 --> 03:32.930
That's how it is.

03:35.800 --> 03:36.650
I see.

03:36.700 --> 03:37.910
So,

03:37.940 --> 03:39.500
Her Ladyship's cold is fake,

03:39.500 --> 03:41.430
but her chronic poisoning is real.

03:42.150 --> 03:44.020
I got it. Thank you.

03:45.640 --> 03:46.750
Leaving already?

03:48.710 --> 03:50.120
Nothing else you want to know?

03:50.120 --> 03:50.910
I know a lot!

03:50.910 --> 03:52.370
I can tell you everything!

03:55.710 --> 03:56.840
Nice.

03:56.860 --> 03:59.320
There's another person protecting Fan Yun.

04:02.690 --> 04:03.720
Fan Yun.

04:04.300 --> 04:05.510
Miss Wei?

04:07.410 --> 04:08.660
Miss Wei.

04:10.200 --> 04:11.170
Where is Suyin?

04:11.830 --> 04:12.790
Suyin?

04:13.760 --> 04:16.890
Suyin said she wasn't feeling well
and went back

04:16.910 --> 04:17.730
to rest.

04:17.750 --> 04:19.350
She asked me to take her place.

04:19.350 --> 04:21.920
Not feeling well?

04:23.040 --> 04:24.270
She's sick?

04:25.210 --> 04:26.480
What's wrong

04:26.890 --> 04:27.960
with Suyin?

04:30.160 --> 04:30.980
I don't know either.

04:30.980 --> 04:32.510
Probably nothing serious.

04:34.240 --> 04:36.000
But Suyin...

04:36.000 --> 04:38.230
Suyin this; Suyin that.

04:38.260 --> 04:39.790
Does the medicine I feed you not work?

04:39.790 --> 04:40.550
Drink it now.

04:42.510 --> 04:44.360
Why are you so fierce?

04:44.680 --> 04:45.870
I'll drink it.

04:54.270 --> 04:55.830
Yuck, it tastes awful.

05:05.990 --> 05:06.920
Miss Wei.

05:07.240 --> 05:09.190
You always

05:09.210 --> 05:11.090
keep your access badge on you, right?

05:11.090 --> 05:11.800
Yes.

05:13.210 --> 05:14.210
Miss Wei,

05:14.360 --> 05:16.160
could you do me a favor?

05:17.650 --> 05:18.650
What favor?

05:18.670 --> 05:19.650
I want to leave the premises.

05:19.650 --> 05:20.820
No way.

05:20.920 --> 05:21.870
You are still sick,

05:21.870 --> 05:23.730
and the governor wouldn't agree.

05:24.560 --> 05:25.560
Anyway, this time,

05:25.560 --> 05:27.210
no one can stop me.

05:27.230 --> 05:28.500
I must go out.

05:28.530 --> 05:29.480
The private school matter

05:29.480 --> 05:30.570
is urgent.

05:30.810 --> 05:31.890
I beg you.

05:31.920 --> 05:32.840
Please help me.

05:32.860 --> 05:34.320
I can't help you with this.

05:38.920 --> 05:39.850
Sister-in-Law.

05:40.500 --> 05:41.230
What is that?

05:41.950 --> 05:42.870
This is

05:42.870 --> 05:45.700
Mr. Gao Ran's personal item.

05:45.810 --> 05:47.540
I wonder if you're interested.

05:50.659 --> 05:51.740
How can I help you?

05:52.810 --> 05:55.250
I want the access badge
the governor gave you.

05:55.250 --> 05:56.250
Here you go!

05:57.350 --> 05:58.350
You're just...

05:59.190 --> 06:00.320
just giving it to me?

06:00.580 --> 06:01.830
Thank you, Miss Wei.

06:02.360 --> 06:03.600
No, thank you.

06:05.070 --> 06:06.270
You're welcome.

06:13.410 --> 06:14.410
Your Excellency.

06:14.920 --> 06:16.000
Why are you back?

06:17.190 --> 06:18.050
I asked around.

06:18.220 --> 06:20.200
The private school just changed owners.

06:20.200 --> 06:21.460
It's nothing serious.

06:21.950 --> 06:24.080
Did you find out
who bought the school?

06:24.610 --> 06:25.830
The buyer is Juyun Pavilion.

06:25.830 --> 06:27.570
We've sent people to buy the land back.

06:27.570 --> 06:28.570
But they

06:28.590 --> 06:30.590
don't seem to want to sell it.

06:32.640 --> 06:33.640
Your Excellency,

06:33.920 --> 06:35.650
there is another small matter.

06:38.190 --> 06:38.920
Speak.

06:40.310 --> 06:42.180
Her Ladyship borrowed
my sister's access badge

06:42.180 --> 06:43.190
to slip out of the residence

06:43.190 --> 06:43.920
despite the danger,

06:43.920 --> 06:45.320
keeping it from all of us.

06:46.120 --> 06:47.050
What did you say?

06:48.740 --> 06:50.230
My Lady left the premises?

06:50.260 --> 06:51.290
Where did she go?

06:51.310 --> 06:52.190
Presumably,

06:52.220 --> 06:54.510
she went to meet the teachers and students
of the private school.

06:54.510 --> 06:55.630
Yan Jiang and I discussed it

06:55.630 --> 06:57.020
and decided not to get in the way.

06:57.020 --> 06:58.080
Where is Yan Jiang?

06:58.870 --> 06:59.680
I came to report her safety first

06:59.680 --> 07:00.600
to put your mind at ease.

07:00.600 --> 07:01.930
Yan Jiang followed her.

07:02.100 --> 07:04.750
That fellow who is bad with directions
is following her?

07:04.750 --> 07:06.040
But Yan Jiang is good at

07:06.040 --> 07:06.890
recognizing faces.

07:06.890 --> 07:07.720
It'll be fine.

07:10.760 --> 07:12.890
Your Excellency, where are you going?

07:14.280 --> 07:15.680
Here you go.

07:16.920 --> 07:18.310
Mother, I want this.

07:34.930 --> 07:35.970
Where is she?

07:36.480 --> 07:40.340
[Qingzhuang Academy]

07:41.630 --> 07:43.580
You must be the teacher Fan Yun.

07:43.710 --> 07:45.100
President Lou invites you.

07:45.100 --> 07:46.460
Please come with us.

07:46.920 --> 07:48.190
President Lou?

07:52.140 --> 07:53.310
I knew it.

07:53.830 --> 07:55.560
You were coming for me.

07:56.510 --> 07:59.409
[Juyun Pavilion]

08:24.280 --> 08:25.640
Young Master Qiyan.

08:29.870 --> 08:31.650
You must have been

08:31.900 --> 08:33.370
waiting for a long time.

08:43.210 --> 08:44.730
May I ask why you

08:44.750 --> 08:46.110
summoned me today?

08:46.140 --> 08:47.350
Please speak your mind.

08:47.350 --> 08:48.160
I'll listen.

08:48.960 --> 08:50.080
Do you know

08:50.100 --> 08:51.610
what kind of huqin this is

08:51.640 --> 08:52.530
in my hands?

09:11.430 --> 09:12.390
This is...

09:12.870 --> 09:14.540
A masterpiece from the previous dynasty,

09:14.540 --> 09:15.910
named the Ancient Moon.

09:19.760 --> 09:21.490
A masterpiece for a beauty.

09:27.030 --> 09:27.910
Please sit.

09:38.390 --> 09:39.240
Young Master,

09:39.930 --> 09:41.650
you didn't just invite me here

09:41.670 --> 09:43.530
to look at an instrument, did you?

09:46.360 --> 09:47.790
It seems you don't plan to

09:48.890 --> 09:51.350
explain about
the incident at Huan'e House.

09:54.840 --> 09:56.510
I offended you that day.

09:56.750 --> 09:58.480
Please let me apologize to you.

09:58.620 --> 10:00.290
I hope you can...

10:04.830 --> 10:06.560
be magnanimous and forgive me.

10:07.120 --> 10:09.720
Please don't take it out
on the private school.

10:09.900 --> 10:11.070
Play a piece first,

10:11.090 --> 10:12.890
and we'll talk about the school.

11:54.870 --> 11:56.720
That's the tune.

11:57.630 --> 11:59.750
The sound is engaging

11:59.750 --> 12:01.120
and majestic.

12:02.630 --> 12:04.600
It gets the blood pumping.

12:06.600 --> 12:09.630
This must be "Absolute Loyalty."

12:22.630 --> 12:25.200
Miss Fan Yun, why did you stop?

12:27.150 --> 12:28.630
Young Master Qiyan.

12:29.270 --> 12:30.960
The name of this piece is

12:30.960 --> 12:33.090
"Listen to Rain on the Mountainside."

12:33.360 --> 12:35.120
The tune is

12:35.120 --> 12:37.840
tranquil, refreshing, and ethereal,

12:37.840 --> 12:39.870
not the blood-pumping

12:39.870 --> 12:42.080
battle song you spoke of.

12:42.840 --> 12:45.360
It seems your ear for music is

12:45.360 --> 12:48.240
really quite extraordinary.

12:58.510 --> 13:00.790
This is our third meeting.

13:00.790 --> 13:03.520
Gold is easy to get,
but a soulmate is hard to find.

13:03.960 --> 13:05.720
I took the liberty of
inviting you here today.

13:05.720 --> 13:07.270
Sorry for startling you.

13:14.150 --> 13:15.210
This is my apology.

13:16.000 --> 13:17.240
From now on, for every piece you play,

13:17.240 --> 13:19.320
I'll grant you one favor in return;

13:19.320 --> 13:20.870
anything at all.

13:24.960 --> 13:26.000
You are

13:26.750 --> 13:29.120
giving this deed to the private school

13:29.120 --> 13:31.790
to me just like that?

13:36.240 --> 13:38.000
Get your claws off her!

13:38.000 --> 13:39.000
Your Excellency?

13:39.320 --> 13:40.720
W-Why are you here?

13:44.200 --> 13:45.670
Did he bully you?

13:45.960 --> 13:47.150
No.

13:49.240 --> 13:50.750
So the governor has arrived.

13:50.750 --> 13:52.480
You sure are brazen, Young Master Lou.

13:52.480 --> 13:55.540
Do you think you can
touch My Lady's hands as you please?

13:57.790 --> 13:59.960
It's a pity I couldn't finish
listening to this piece.

13:59.960 --> 14:02.560
Although we feel differently
about the piece,

14:02.790 --> 14:04.660
your skills are indeed exquisite.

14:04.660 --> 14:05.940
I really like them.

14:07.790 --> 14:09.120
Thank you, Young Master Qiyan.

14:09.120 --> 14:10.850
You even played a piece for him?

14:11.020 --> 14:11.770
Look.

14:14.720 --> 14:16.040
Good that you liked it.

14:16.400 --> 14:18.120
But there won't be a next time.

14:18.690 --> 14:20.430
Apologies for my poor hospitality,
Your Excellency.

14:20.430 --> 14:22.140
Just as mountains and rivers
eventually cross,

14:22.140 --> 14:23.560
may our paths cross again.

14:23.560 --> 14:25.090
People who walk different paths
aren't a good fit.

14:25.090 --> 14:26.250
See you never.

14:28.840 --> 14:29.870
Miss Fan Yun.

14:31.030 --> 14:32.380
We will meet again.

14:33.750 --> 14:35.390
The students will thank you!

14:35.890 --> 14:36.830
Your Excellency.

14:36.830 --> 14:38.520
I only sneaked out

14:38.600 --> 14:40.960
because I was worried
about the private school.

14:40.960 --> 14:42.750
Hey, it hurts!

15:07.440 --> 15:08.480
Your Excellency.

15:08.760 --> 15:10.160
Do you want a snack?

15:11.390 --> 15:12.630
It's delicious.

15:13.740 --> 15:14.700
Try one.

15:24.430 --> 15:25.850
Your Excellency, what are you doing?

15:25.850 --> 15:27.910
Which hand did Lou Qiyan use
to hold yours?

15:27.910 --> 15:28.540
I...

15:28.690 --> 15:30.120
He schemed in every way
to get close to you;

15:30.120 --> 15:31.530
even bought the private school for you.

15:31.530 --> 15:33.120
He clearly has ulterior motives.

15:33.120 --> 15:35.250
So, of course I have to wipe them clean.

15:37.000 --> 15:38.670
Y-You know everything?

15:39.510 --> 15:42.100
Of course I sent Wei and Yan out
to investigate.

15:42.100 --> 15:43.770
You even used a honey trap!

15:43.800 --> 15:44.800
I didn't!

15:44.870 --> 15:45.480
Don't you

15:45.480 --> 15:47.680
trust me to resolve the problem for you?

15:48.000 --> 15:48.670
I...

15:49.870 --> 15:51.390
I trust you.

15:52.550 --> 15:53.790
Well, he gave me

15:53.790 --> 15:55.460
the deed to the private school.

15:55.460 --> 15:56.750
We aren't losing out,

15:56.840 --> 15:57.440
are we?

15:57.910 --> 15:58.750
Right?

15:58.750 --> 15:59.600
I'll break his legs

15:59.600 --> 16:00.770
if he dares to take advantage of you!

16:00.770 --> 16:03.080
Speaking of Lou Qiyan makes my blood boil.

16:03.080 --> 16:04.630
All merchants are dishonest.

16:04.630 --> 16:05.480
He gave you this school,

16:05.480 --> 16:07.480
so he must want something in return.

16:08.270 --> 16:09.780
Don't tell me he's trading it for you!

16:09.780 --> 16:10.460
Me?

16:10.480 --> 16:12.250
How could I give myself to him?

16:12.280 --> 16:13.400
B-Besides,

16:13.440 --> 16:14.200
it's not like

16:14.200 --> 16:16.040
he can do whatever he wants.

16:16.270 --> 16:18.270
What are you thinking?

16:22.570 --> 16:23.860
Your Excellency.

16:23.890 --> 16:24.890
After all,

16:24.910 --> 16:27.340
those are students
who have been seeking my guidance.

16:27.340 --> 16:29.600
The private school is my life's work too.

16:29.780 --> 16:31.070
Also,

16:31.100 --> 16:32.770
if that Lou Qiyan

16:32.790 --> 16:34.160
wanted to harm me,

16:34.240 --> 16:35.440
he could've just found a random place

16:35.440 --> 16:36.840
in the streets to bury me.

16:36.920 --> 16:39.640
That would also reduce suspicion
against Juyun Pavilion.

16:39.640 --> 16:40.310
Right?

16:42.670 --> 16:44.280
I guess that makes sense.

16:47.250 --> 16:48.330
All right then.

16:48.660 --> 16:50.230
I'll believe you this once.

16:50.480 --> 16:51.950
Now,

16:52.440 --> 16:53.750
can you have the snack?

16:54.530 --> 16:55.460
Try it.

16:56.050 --> 16:57.170
It's really good.

17:03.600 --> 17:04.369
Whatever!

17:05.890 --> 17:07.140
Forget about him.

17:07.359 --> 17:08.560
He's bad luck anyway.

17:08.829 --> 17:09.750
I need to go home now

17:09.750 --> 17:11.390
to sign the documents Lord Zheng left me

17:11.390 --> 17:12.940
for raising taxes.

17:13.329 --> 17:14.400
Raising taxes?

17:19.750 --> 17:21.079
It's a stopgap measure.

17:21.310 --> 17:22.170
But

17:22.380 --> 17:23.700
is it right?

17:24.550 --> 17:27.119
The most important thing in Nine Cities
is its people.

17:27.119 --> 17:28.840
Blindly raising taxes

17:28.860 --> 17:30.430
will only make the people suffer

17:30.430 --> 17:32.290
and destabilize the Nine Cities.

17:35.720 --> 17:36.720
Your Excellency,

17:37.120 --> 17:38.580
let me take you somewhere.

17:39.390 --> 17:40.150
Turn around!

17:40.410 --> 17:42.210
To the Alley Literary Teahouse.

17:48.070 --> 17:51.750
[Alley Literary Teahouse]

17:48.430 --> 17:49.560
Have you heard?

17:49.580 --> 17:52.040
They're raising taxes
in Nine Cities again.

17:52.200 --> 17:53.400
How can small businesses

17:53.400 --> 17:54.920
like ours keep running?

17:55.210 --> 17:56.690
We have families to feed.

17:56.710 --> 17:57.610
This literary teahouse

17:57.610 --> 17:59.540
has been here since I was born.

17:59.560 --> 18:00.800
I know it won't work!

18:00.830 --> 18:02.160
Hidden talents abound here.

18:02.160 --> 18:04.420
Everyone inside is very knowledgeable.

18:06.900 --> 18:08.090
Do you still remember

18:08.090 --> 18:09.890
the flood in Gao City 5 years ago?

18:11.350 --> 18:12.400
Remember?

18:12.400 --> 18:13.340
At that time,

18:13.360 --> 18:14.600
many people

18:14.630 --> 18:16.720
came here to ask them for advice.

18:17.770 --> 18:18.590
Not to mention you lot...

18:18.590 --> 18:19.830
The man on the left,

18:19.830 --> 18:20.900
he sells silk.

18:21.370 --> 18:22.350
That man in the middle

18:22.350 --> 18:23.310
sells pork.

18:23.440 --> 18:24.970
They are all very talented.

18:25.430 --> 18:27.790
Don't underestimate them
because they are commoners;

18:27.790 --> 18:29.190
each and every one of them

18:29.200 --> 18:30.780
cares deeply about the Nine Cities

18:30.780 --> 18:31.970
and its people.

18:32.000 --> 18:34.400
There must be a limit
to taking the people's

18:34.530 --> 18:35.730
wealth and hard work.

18:36.530 --> 18:38.020
The imposition of taxes and labor

18:38.020 --> 18:39.740
cannot be unbridled.

18:40.060 --> 18:40.730
Otherwise,

18:42.190 --> 18:42.920
we

18:43.060 --> 18:44.500
and the entire Nine Cities

18:44.500 --> 18:46.540
will be like a runaway carriage,

18:47.100 --> 18:48.570
our fortunes taking a nosedive.

18:48.570 --> 18:49.960
In my opinion, historically,

18:49.960 --> 18:52.920
periods of prosperity are built on
minimal taxation and corvée labor.

18:52.920 --> 18:54.550
There were no miscellaneous charges,

18:54.550 --> 18:56.270
and the land tax was reasonable.

18:56.270 --> 18:57.540
Nothing complicated;

18:57.570 --> 18:59.200
the commoners only needed to hand over

18:59.200 --> 19:01.000
a portion of their annual grain.

19:01.030 --> 19:02.400
If such taxes

19:02.400 --> 19:03.820
only account for 10%,

19:03.930 --> 19:05.960
then such an excellent policy
of recuperation is

19:05.960 --> 19:08.890
most beneficial to
improving people's livelihood.

19:10.510 --> 19:11.510
Your Excellency,

19:12.090 --> 19:13.620
will you still raise taxes?

19:16.550 --> 19:17.960
Did you think I wanted to

19:18.370 --> 19:20.030
raise the taxes of the people?

19:23.130 --> 19:23.840
What do you

19:23.950 --> 19:24.830
mean by that?

19:27.200 --> 19:28.200
What do you think?

19:30.480 --> 19:33.080
You said earlier
that it was a stopgap measure.

19:33.200 --> 19:34.060
What about now?

19:36.320 --> 19:37.320
What do you think?

19:41.230 --> 19:42.430
What I think?

19:43.200 --> 19:44.440
I think you

19:44.460 --> 19:46.260
don't want to raise taxes,

19:46.290 --> 19:48.150
and even have a desire for reform.

19:49.070 --> 19:51.120
If you didn't
have the welfare of the people at heart,

19:51.120 --> 19:52.270
you wouldn't have come with me

19:52.270 --> 19:53.800
to that literary teahouse.

19:54.340 --> 19:56.490
Your so-called incompetence

19:57.040 --> 19:58.880
is just an act you put on, right?

20:08.770 --> 20:09.850
Fan Yun.

20:10.550 --> 20:12.750
The mind of a sovereign is inscrutable.

20:13.400 --> 20:14.090
Is it?

20:14.920 --> 20:15.920
Could it be

20:16.680 --> 20:18.280
that this isn't the real you?

20:21.110 --> 20:22.240
What about you?

20:22.870 --> 20:23.950
Knowing all this,

20:24.770 --> 20:27.430
you still cooperate with me
despite the danger.

20:28.150 --> 20:28.890
Yes.

20:29.480 --> 20:30.810
It's because I know everything

20:30.810 --> 20:32.090
that I'm willing.

20:35.240 --> 20:37.240
Because this is also what I want.

20:39.110 --> 20:40.330
I've thought about it.

20:40.330 --> 20:41.540
After we go back,

20:41.570 --> 20:43.700
I'll keep doing my best
to cooperate with you.

20:43.700 --> 20:45.050
I won't cause you trouble

20:45.050 --> 20:47.510
and will let you
leverage my power steadily.

21:09.960 --> 21:10.700
Wei Ying.

21:11.270 --> 21:13.330
Why is my pay so much lower this month?

21:14.790 --> 21:16.020
Shouldn't every official

21:16.020 --> 21:18.020
know about the increased taxation?

21:19.610 --> 21:20.940
Did I misunderstand it?

21:21.990 --> 21:24.190
Weren't we raising taxes on the people?

21:26.400 --> 21:28.530
Raising taxes is an incompetent move.

21:28.600 --> 21:29.800
I was also worried

21:29.880 --> 21:31.070
the governor was acting on a whim

21:31.070 --> 21:32.320
without forethought.

21:32.320 --> 21:33.270
But after

21:33.510 --> 21:35.420
the tax adjustments were
announced to the public,

21:35.420 --> 21:37.010
I realized I was overthinking it.

21:37.010 --> 21:37.730
Look,

21:38.300 --> 21:39.890
this tax increase only applies to

21:39.890 --> 21:41.990
those with a monthly income
of over 5 tons of grain.

21:41.990 --> 21:43.610
Other taxes remain unchanged.

21:43.610 --> 21:44.670
There are even some

21:44.950 --> 21:47.390
tax reductions and exemptions
for commoners.

21:47.390 --> 21:48.660
Over 5 tons...

21:50.590 --> 21:53.650
That's based on the salary
of a seventh-rank official.

21:54.660 --> 21:56.500
And the agricultural income of the nobles

21:56.500 --> 21:58.300
basically meets this standard.

22:01.670 --> 22:02.720
I see.

22:02.740 --> 22:04.200
The governor is trying to

22:04.810 --> 22:07.270
take advantage of
the officials and nobles.

22:12.740 --> 22:15.180
Such a tax reform is

22:15.200 --> 22:17.760
going to... to be the death of me!

22:17.790 --> 22:18.920
I... I...

22:26.030 --> 22:26.920
I recognize that

22:26.920 --> 22:28.310
the empty treasury this year

22:28.310 --> 22:29.260
is a major issue.

22:29.840 --> 22:30.830
But this year has been

22:30.830 --> 22:32.190
a year of poor harvest!

22:32.210 --> 22:32.770
That's right!

22:32.770 --> 22:34.680
The commoners can't afford to pay taxes,

22:34.680 --> 22:36.440
but we nobles don't have

22:36.470 --> 22:37.930
any surplus grain either.

22:38.230 --> 22:39.950
-Am I right?
-Totally!

22:40.060 --> 22:41.690
-Exactly!
-Exactly!

22:41.720 --> 22:43.090
I used to enjoy

22:43.440 --> 22:45.240
20 dishes for a meal.

22:45.960 --> 22:47.070
Now,

22:47.880 --> 22:50.310
I only have 12 dishes!

22:51.170 --> 22:52.570
Lord Fan, look at me!

22:52.600 --> 22:54.770
I'm wasting away!

22:55.830 --> 22:57.720
-This tax increase...
-Yes.

22:57.720 --> 23:01.200
Why is it targeting the nobles?

23:01.200 --> 23:04.070
Were the commoners' taxes even raised?

23:04.090 --> 23:04.900
Goodness...

23:04.380 --> 23:07.870
[Duanyun Gate]

23:08.770 --> 23:10.920
Last time Lord Zheng
suggested raising taxes

23:10.920 --> 23:12.120
to fill the treasury,

23:12.590 --> 23:13.960
I strongly agreed.

23:15.180 --> 23:16.610
I didn't expect

23:17.110 --> 23:19.710
the implemented draft
to cause such an uproar.

23:24.550 --> 23:25.550
Your Excellency.

23:25.850 --> 23:27.140
I believe

23:27.870 --> 23:31.920
the tax regulations
currently implemented in Nine Cities

23:32.550 --> 23:35.840
are different from what I presented.

23:36.280 --> 23:37.840
-So...
-Lord Zheng.

23:39.360 --> 23:40.790
Now you're aware that

23:40.830 --> 23:43.370
raising taxes causes an uproar.

23:43.530 --> 23:46.120
The current situation is
already so volatile.

23:46.120 --> 23:48.120
Raising taxes on the commoners now

23:48.140 --> 23:49.930
will surely provoke public outrage.

23:49.930 --> 23:50.780
You...

23:50.810 --> 23:51.590
Enough.

23:53.110 --> 23:55.150
I'm also in a difficult position.

24:03.310 --> 24:04.840
My dear lords, to be honest,

24:05.750 --> 24:07.410
I've been tossing and turning

24:07.770 --> 24:09.810
because of this matter these days.

24:11.080 --> 24:12.210
But just last night,

24:12.770 --> 24:15.030
I actually dreamed of the late governor.

24:15.070 --> 24:18.730
So I asked the late governor, my father,
for advice on governance.

24:19.830 --> 24:21.270
And guess what?

24:21.440 --> 24:22.830
When the late governor heard

24:22.830 --> 24:24.860
that I was actually
worrying about the people,

24:24.860 --> 24:25.930
he was overjoyed!

24:26.550 --> 24:28.280
So he proposed a strategy to me:

24:28.650 --> 24:30.760
open up trade in Nine Cities.

24:31.350 --> 24:33.300
Ji City is rich in steel.

24:33.680 --> 24:35.740
Gao City is abound with fish and rice.

24:35.830 --> 24:38.760
Wang City's porcelain is world-famous.

24:38.990 --> 24:41.520
Every city has its own specialty.

24:42.030 --> 24:43.430
With the treasury empty,

24:43.940 --> 24:45.090
trade,

24:45.200 --> 24:45.930
road repair,

24:46.240 --> 24:47.450
and agricultural support

24:47.450 --> 24:48.980
are all viable paths.

24:49.790 --> 24:51.070
If trade routes are opened

24:51.070 --> 24:52.980
and cities can trade freely,

24:53.570 --> 24:55.920
then with the circulation
of money and daily necessities,

24:55.920 --> 24:58.040
the people will naturally
become prosperous.

24:58.040 --> 24:59.990
When we raise taxes then,

25:00.400 --> 25:02.730
there wouldn't be any livelihood issues.

25:04.050 --> 25:05.490
When I woke up,

25:05.860 --> 25:06.670
I thought

25:06.700 --> 25:08.900
it was brilliant; truly enlightening!

25:09.230 --> 25:10.230
Lord Zheng,

25:11.310 --> 25:13.000
what do you think?

25:13.960 --> 25:15.810
A dream from the late governor;

25:16.350 --> 25:17.540
this strategy

25:17.900 --> 25:19.300
is good indeed.

25:19.830 --> 25:22.160
But Your Excellency, have you considered

25:22.710 --> 25:23.990
that a slow remedy

25:24.500 --> 25:27.090
does not address the current emergency?

25:27.150 --> 25:28.190
Besides,

25:28.210 --> 25:31.410
it's just an armchair strategy!

25:31.440 --> 25:32.520
Lord Zheng.

25:34.200 --> 25:36.070
You certainly consider things

25:36.070 --> 25:39.480
more thoroughly than the late governor.

25:39.480 --> 25:41.440
But do you have

25:41.780 --> 25:44.890
a better solution than the late governor?

25:47.250 --> 25:51.120
I'm merely doing my best
for the Nine Cities.

25:52.780 --> 25:55.650
Please make the decision, Your Excellency.

26:14.390 --> 26:16.390
Invoking the late governor

26:16.410 --> 26:17.860
to leave me speechless?

26:17.890 --> 26:20.000
Qi Zheng has never dared to

26:20.020 --> 26:21.680
defy me in political matters.

26:22.440 --> 26:24.700
How did he come up with such an idea now?

26:28.430 --> 26:30.160
The other day, the spy said

26:30.240 --> 26:31.400
that he saw

26:31.420 --> 26:35.030
the governor returning to his residence
with Fan Yun.

26:35.520 --> 26:38.630
Could this be her doing again?

26:39.790 --> 26:41.190
Qi Zheng is the governor,

26:41.920 --> 26:43.790
but he is actually allowing himself

26:43.790 --> 26:45.280
to be manipulated.

26:45.620 --> 26:48.830
What utter foolishness and incompetence!

26:48.860 --> 26:50.750
Please calm down, Master.

26:50.910 --> 26:52.150
Who knew

26:52.170 --> 26:53.690
that witch Fan Yun

26:53.720 --> 26:55.110
would become so intimate

26:55.110 --> 26:56.460
with the governor so quickly?

26:56.460 --> 26:58.570
What's the use of blaming it
all on a woman?

26:58.570 --> 26:59.590
The root of the problem

26:59.590 --> 27:01.650
lies in that good-for-nothing man!

27:02.200 --> 27:04.110
He is unfit for the position!

27:04.110 --> 27:06.170
Master, be cautious with your words.

27:06.180 --> 27:07.580
He's just lucky to be born

27:07.810 --> 27:10.430
with the Qi family's blood in his veins.

27:16.470 --> 27:17.630
Do you mean he is

27:18.620 --> 27:21.070
Qingyuan, the Second Young Master Qi?

27:24.200 --> 27:25.920
Qi Zheng had been

27:26.530 --> 27:28.460
fooling around in the Nine Cities.

27:31.070 --> 27:33.480
When the late governor was alive,

27:35.830 --> 27:37.380
the favored heir

27:38.300 --> 27:40.040
was not him.

27:41.060 --> 27:42.580
So you're saying...

27:55.070 --> 27:56.310
Knowing all this,

27:56.960 --> 27:59.270
you still cooperate with me
despite the danger.

27:59.270 --> 28:00.510
Yes.

28:00.540 --> 28:01.990
It's because I know everything

28:01.990 --> 28:03.230
that I'm willing.

28:03.730 --> 28:06.060
Then cooperate with me on one thing first.

28:06.730 --> 28:07.650
Poisoning?

28:08.920 --> 28:11.370
Who would poison me in my bedchamber?

28:15.810 --> 28:16.920
Fan Yun,

28:16.940 --> 28:19.710
I just learned a makeup look
that is all the rage.

28:19.880 --> 28:20.940
Let me try it on you.

28:21.250 --> 28:22.480
Between close friends,

28:22.480 --> 28:25.240
beauty secrets shouldn't be hidden.

28:29.510 --> 28:30.680
Fan Yun?

28:32.200 --> 28:32.930
Fan Yun!

28:35.030 --> 28:35.830
What is it?

28:35.830 --> 28:36.620
What's wrong with you?

28:36.620 --> 28:38.270
Are you ready?

28:38.330 --> 28:39.800
Then let's stick to the plan

28:39.800 --> 28:41.260
and start the sick makeup.

28:42.270 --> 28:43.090
I'm fine.

28:44.130 --> 28:45.260
Time for the makeup.

28:48.380 --> 28:49.030
Come on.

29:16.640 --> 29:18.040
Everything's spinning.

29:18.430 --> 29:19.350
Somebody help!

29:19.810 --> 29:21.070
Her Ladyship has fainted! Come!

29:21.070 --> 29:22.270
Hurry, hurry!

29:40.830 --> 29:42.260
You're pretty quick.

29:43.970 --> 29:45.690
I barely had to wait at all.

30:17.850 --> 30:18.640
Suyin.

30:19.480 --> 30:20.170
Look at me.

30:23.720 --> 30:25.170
Did you poison her?

30:31.770 --> 30:32.950
No one ordered me to do it.

30:32.950 --> 30:34.600
I did it myself.

30:36.700 --> 30:37.840
Don't be nervous.

30:38.930 --> 30:40.060
Let me ask you again.

30:40.630 --> 30:42.250
Fan Yun treats you so well.

30:43.500 --> 30:45.790
Why did you repeatedly poison her?

30:46.960 --> 30:49.000
My Lady... My Lady...

30:49.110 --> 30:50.520
Is My Lady alright?

30:50.810 --> 30:52.270
Since you did it yourself,

30:52.600 --> 30:54.730
why do you care if she is alright or not?

30:56.310 --> 30:58.050
I administered the poison,

30:58.930 --> 31:00.550
but I didn't want her to die.

31:00.710 --> 31:02.040
-Then why...
-Wei Ying.

31:04.110 --> 31:05.110
Get up first.

31:26.140 --> 31:27.400
Where is Her Ladyship?

31:33.740 --> 31:34.980
Your Excellency.

31:38.690 --> 31:39.410
Oh no.

32:01.400 --> 32:02.290
Anything?

32:03.050 --> 32:03.980
Your Excellency,

32:03.980 --> 32:06.580
I have deployed men
to search for Her Ladyship.

32:13.410 --> 32:14.670
Protect the governor!

32:17.290 --> 32:18.980
A squad will stay with me
to protect the governor.

32:18.980 --> 32:20.310
The rest, go after them!

32:20.360 --> 32:22.960
-Let's go! After them!
-Get a move on! Let's go!

32:28.480 --> 32:31.550
[If you wish to save her, come to
Linglong Tower alone. Fan Yun is here.]

32:29.710 --> 32:31.430
To think they'd be so rampant.

32:31.450 --> 32:32.850
Who knows what they want?

32:33.310 --> 32:34.310
Her Ladyship...

32:34.950 --> 32:36.280
might be in danger.

32:37.700 --> 32:38.870
Linglong Tower...

32:41.660 --> 32:44.380
Wei Ying, go find Gao Ran.

32:44.410 --> 32:46.170
Tell him to notify Lord Fan Qi.

32:48.440 --> 32:49.320
Lord Fan Qi.

32:59.510 --> 33:00.510
Dark Wolf!

33:02.200 --> 33:03.030
Dark Wolf!

33:12.570 --> 33:13.740
Lord Fan Qi.

33:14.330 --> 33:15.770
What are you doing?

33:16.710 --> 33:18.150
Wolf! Wolf!

33:18.170 --> 33:18.800
Wolf?

33:23.330 --> 33:24.850
Your Excellency,

33:24.880 --> 33:28.130
so you were just trying to scare me.

33:28.600 --> 33:29.490
What wolf?

33:29.520 --> 33:31.320
There are no wolves in this area.

33:31.400 --> 33:33.410
Your Excellency, if you're here,

33:33.670 --> 33:35.360
does it mean Yun is back too?

33:35.900 --> 33:38.560
I came back specifically to see you,
Lord Fan Qi.

33:39.570 --> 33:41.660
I'll prepare tea for you right away.

33:41.690 --> 33:42.150
Hang on.

33:44.370 --> 33:45.570
Lord Fan Qi.

33:46.980 --> 33:49.610
Isn't your acting a bit over the top?

33:54.740 --> 33:55.820
It's you, isn't it?

33:56.470 --> 33:57.340
Me?

33:58.290 --> 34:00.600
W-What... What do you mean?

34:11.949 --> 34:13.610
You see, a perfectly good tree

34:14.130 --> 34:16.060
that could have lived for a century

34:16.560 --> 34:18.130
has now met with disaster.

34:19.830 --> 34:20.860
Lord Fan Qi.

34:21.739 --> 34:23.870
If the roots of this tree are withered,

34:24.449 --> 34:25.719
how should it be saved?

34:26.429 --> 34:27.639
Water it

34:27.760 --> 34:28.760
and fertilize it.

34:29.190 --> 34:30.610
If the roots are rotten,

34:31.070 --> 34:31.790
what then?

34:32.469 --> 34:33.620
Uproot it,

34:33.920 --> 34:36.290
prune the rot, and rejuvenate the soil.

34:36.310 --> 34:38.110
That's exactly what I wish to do.

34:38.520 --> 34:39.880
Today's Nine Cities

34:40.210 --> 34:42.469
is just like this withered phoenix tree,

34:43.179 --> 34:44.780
decaying and conservative.

34:44.800 --> 34:47.840
If we don't nourish it,
prune the rot, and rejuvenate the soil,

34:47.840 --> 34:49.300
it won't be able to grow new buds

34:49.300 --> 34:50.550
and bear fruit again.

34:52.230 --> 34:53.290
I really don't want

34:54.070 --> 34:56.120
this tree to die in my hands.

34:56.650 --> 34:57.710
Do you understand?

34:59.060 --> 34:59.860
I understand.

35:03.110 --> 35:04.770
It's fine if you don't trust me

35:05.570 --> 35:06.530
right now.

35:07.170 --> 35:08.460
I'll pretend I bought

35:09.150 --> 35:10.880
this paper knife at the market.

35:12.910 --> 35:14.640
Although I like the look of it,

35:15.820 --> 35:17.550
I don't want to take it by force.

35:17.950 --> 35:19.480
Let's test its sharpness.

35:21.780 --> 35:23.380
I'll take this paper with me;

35:23.400 --> 35:26.250
I hope to have your help in the future.

35:48.750 --> 35:49.710
Let's go.

36:13.120 --> 36:14.540
Where am I?

36:16.440 --> 36:17.680
Is anyone there?

36:17.850 --> 36:19.250
Help!

36:21.440 --> 36:22.400
Help!

36:34.970 --> 36:35.970
You...

36:39.240 --> 36:40.630
Who are you?
